<p><b>Preparedness</b>:<br>
Visit <a href="http://www.cobbanddouglaspublichealth.org">CobbAndDouglasPublicHealth.org</a>, for preparedness tips for both the workplace and residents of the community. Another good resource is the CDC website: <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/index.html">cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/community/index.html</a></p>

<p><b>Travel</b>:<br>
